\c 114
\s Simba raJehovha parwendo rwevaIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Pakubuda kwaIsraeri paEgipita, imba yaJakove pavanhu verurimi rwevechirudzi,
\v 2 Judha wakava imba yake tsvene, Israeri \add akava\add* ushe hwake ukuru.
\p
\v 3 Gungwa rakaona ndokutiza; Joridhani rwakadzokera shure.
\v 4 Makomo akapembera semakondohwe; zvikomo semakwayana.
\p
\v 5 Chii kwauri, gungwa, kuti utize? Iwe Joridhani, \add kuti\add* udzokere shure?
\v 6 Imwi makomo, \add kuti\add* munopembera semakondohwe? Imwi zvikomo, semakwayana?
\p
\v 7 Bvunda iwe pasi, pamberi paShe, pamberi paMwari waJakove,
\v 8 wakashandura dombo \add kuva\add* dziva remvura, dombo rakaoma kuva chitubu chemvura zhinji.